data.title: Not what I expected
data.text: Not a blues club nor is it named Dr. Rockits ..it's a country western bar in a not so safe looking area.  $23 for 2 shots and 1 drink which weren't that good. Bummer! Bartender was friendly though!

data.title: Bad bar tenders
data.text: This bar gave terrible service  and I say that because anyone who knows the taste of a good Wild Turkey ...wel theres had alot to ne desired ....super water down  ....I only had two and sorry NO buzz....and God  save the band ..their last set was very depressing songs... other  than that .. cute  and beauitful women ....

data.title: Decent, but not what I expected.
data.text:
It's supposed to be a blues bar but they played everything but seems like. 
They don't serve the alcohol that I like (Hypnotiq).  
And some of my drink was spilled. The waitress did her job, but her attitude...I felt she could have been more hospitable.

data.title: This place oozes cool!
data.text: Great music and atmosphere. The drinks were good and the beer cold. Comfortable seating when you get there early enough. Overall cool place to hang out.

data.title: GREAT BLUES......
data.text: When we're in town we have to go here....best blues around...always rockin! We've been here lots of times, even on our Honeymoon but never a dull moment here......

data.title: Great night out! Music and drinks.
data.text: Lots of fun. Great music and people. Drinks not overpriced. Often have exceptional entertainers. Best on Saturday night.

data.title: Blues joint-kind of divey, but that's how it should be.
data.text:
This place is actually not Dr Rockits any more, it's Rockit's Whiskey Bar.  However, they have kept the live music and, most importantly for Corpus, the blues.  
I came by for free drinks and apps with a group of co-workers, so was really early-4pm.  Music doesn't start til about 9. Still, there was a fair sprinkling of customers around, everyone seemed happy, and the associates were all sparkly and ready to take whatever order we had. I liked the  vibe, and will be coming back when there's actually live music.

data.title: Live Music
data.text: Always original and great bands playing. Its a must every year we visit. Drinks are reasonably priced.

data.title: You want blues?  You got it here......
data.text: Blues every day.  That's the deal here.  The owners don't try to appease all audiences.  They know what they like, what their customers want, and they stick with it!
